results.description:
Retired tiger in Malkia Park. 
Mission of the civic association Malkia Park is to save feline (cat) species from circuses and other inappropriate conditions found in private breeding programs and zoos. Other animal species that have been abused or rejected have also found sanctuary here. Unfortunately, these animals would not be able to survive in the wild, and so, with the help of private funding, park provides them ideal conditions to have a new and dignified life.
(https://www.malkiapark.sk/en/)
